<div style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path('skytop.png') %>'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: fixed" class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-20 pb-20">
  <div class="text-center px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-10 text-white drop-shadow-lg">
      SkyPhotos
    </h1>
    <div class="text-base md:text-lg mb-8 font-light leading-loose text-white drop-shadow-md max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-4">
      <p>忙しい毎日でも、空はいつもそこにある。</p>
      <p>なにげなく見上げた空が心に響く瞬間ありませんか？</p>
      <p>SkyPhotosはふと心に響いた空の写真を共有するアプリです。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-8">
        <%= link_to '空を見上げる', posts_path, class: 'px-8 py-3 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-sky-600 font-semibold rounded-full shadow-lg border-2 border-sky-500 transition duration-300 text-center' %>
    </div>
    <!-- 特徴セクション -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- 投稿 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <%= image_tag "takepicture.png", alt: "写真を撮影", class: "w-32 h-32" %>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-800">写真を投稿</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <p>心に響く空の写真に出会ったら、</p>
          <p>その時感じた気持ちを残そう。</p>
          <p>本文は空欄でもOK</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- emoボタン -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <%= image_tag "heart.png", alt: "エモボタン", class: "w-32 h-32" %>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-800">エモいを表現</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <p>みんなの空の投稿をみて心に響いたら</p>
          <p>エモいボタンで気持ちを伝えよう。</p>
          <p>何度でも押せます。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- お気に入り登録 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <%= image_tag "favorite.png", alt: "お気に入り登録できる", class: "w-32 h-32" %>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-800">お気に入り登録</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <p>お気に入り登録して、</p>
          <p>あなただけの空の写真</p>
          <p>コレクションを作ろう。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>